South Africa to Build $2.2 Billion Rare Metals Plant, Business Report Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-07T05:03:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/south-africa-to-build-2-2-billion-rare-metals-plant-business-report-says.html
South Africa  plans to establish a 15
billion-rand rare-metals industrial complex in the Western Cape
province, Business Report said, citing Trade and Industry
Minister Rob Davies.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
